text.section:
The board shall issue the appropriate establishment license to an applicant who:
Has paid to the board an establishment license fee, not to exceed two hundred dollars ($200), as set out in administrative regulations promulgated by the board; and
Has filed with the board a sworn statement that sets out the following:
Name of the funeral establishment;
Address of the funeral establishment;
Type of funeral establishment;
Owners of the funeral establishment, indicating which owners are licensed by the board; and
Name and address of the Kentucky-licensed embalmer or the Kentucky-licensed funeral director who will supervise the funeral establishment pursuant to subsection (4) of this section.
